1. Introduction
Welcome to Kids Coloring Book: Draw & Paint ("the App"). This App is designed for young children, including children under the age of 5. We are deeply committed to protecting the privacy and safety of all children who use this App.

This Privacy Policy explains what information is collected, how it is used, and what rights parents and guardians have. Please read it carefully.

2. Who This App Is For
This App is designed for children of all ages, including children under 5 years old. It is intended to be used under parental supervision. We comply with:

COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act, USA)
GDPR-K (General Data Protection Regulation for children, EU)
Google Play Families Policy
Google Play Data Safety requirements
3. Information We Do NOT Collect
We believe the best policy for a children's app is to collect as little data as possible. We do not collect:

❌ Name, age, or date of birth
❌ Email address or phone number
❌ Photos, videos, or files from your device
❌ Location or GPS data
❌ Contacts or address book
❌ Microphone or camera input
❌ Device identifiers (IMEI, MAC address)
❌ Login credentials or account information
❌ Any personal information from children
4. Information That May Be Collected Automatically (Advertising)
This App uses Google AdMob to display banner advertisements. AdMob may collect limited, non-personal, technical data to serve ads. Because this App is directed at children, we have configured AdMob to operate in child-directed treatment mode, which means:

No behavioural or interest-based advertising is shown
No personal data is used for ad targeting
Only non-personalized, child-safe ads are displayed
No ad identifiers (GAID/IDFA) are used for profiling children
For more information, see Google's Privacy Policy and Google Families Ads Policy.

5. Artwork & Saved Content
Artwork created in the App is saved only to the device's local storage
Artwork is never uploaded to any server or cloud service
We cannot access, view, or collect any artwork created by your child
Deleting the App removes all locally saved artwork
6. No Account Required
This App does not require:

Creating an account
Signing in
Providing any personal information whatsoever
A child can use the full App without any registration.

7. No Third-Party Sharing
We do not sell, rent, trade, or share any user data with third parties, except as described in Section 4 (AdMob child-directed ads). We have no analytics SDKs, social media SDKs, or tracking SDKs in this App.

8. In-App Purchases
This App does not offer any in-app purchases, subscriptions, or paid unlocks.

9. Parental Controls & Settings
The App includes a Parent Settings section protected by a simple PIN. Through Parent Settings, parents/guardians can:

Manage profiles and themes
Control accessibility options
Review and delete saved artwork from the gallery
We encourage parents to explore the Settings section to customise the experience for their child.

