11. Children Under 5 – Special Protections
Because this App targets children under 5 years old, we apply the following additional protections:

No data collection of any kind from the child
No external links that could navigate a child away from the App (except inside the locked Parent Settings area)
No social features – no chat, comments, sharing to social media, or user-generated content sharing
No push notifications sent to the device
Child-safe ads only via AdMob child-directed treatment — no violent, adult, or inappropriate ad content
No in-app purchases accessible to children without parental action
All content (coloring templates, colors, sounds) is age-appropriate and reviewed for suitability for children under 5
